room_title: Escape room "Ghostbusters: Dimension VR" by The Void Las Vegas in Las Vegas
room_address: 3377 S Las Vegas Blvd #2235 Las Vegas, NV 89109
room_description: Dr. Ray Stantz, Director of Recruitment Research and Trainee Certification, needs your help! An old apartment building in New York’s Garment District is being haunted by an ancient ghost. You and your friends and family will strap on a positron collider and bust any ghosts you find in the apartment. It’s your turn… to be a Ghostbuster!
